            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "请住手！不要再伤害\\n巴尔库斯哥哥了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "如果你那么想战斗，\\n要和我一起走吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "开什么玩笑！\\n你在打什么主意！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "别误会。\\n即使我在这里取你性命，\\n也没有任何意义。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "你的死并不会带给\\n世界的反叛任何影响。\\n我只是不希望这样而已。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "……\\n奈迪犹，你到底……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "就算对立场不同的人解释\\n也不会得到理解。\\n了解真相、自己领悟吧。",
