            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "我要……和你决斗，\\n然后打倒你。一定要——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "为此，什么事我都能忍受。\\n即使忍辱负重、被你嘲笑，\\n我也在所不惜……",
